      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOLLY'S MY MUM (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 530m behind Quick Strike (31.45) in a Grade 6. Was a winner the start prior. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Has ability and can bounce back. HIJINKERY (4) used the inside draw to advantage last time and hit the ground running with a fast early split, but could manage only the minor money when a nose second at this track over 530m in 30.87. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. CLAYMORE LASS (8) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from four tries. Missed the frame latest (26.00) when fifth over 455m at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6. Can feature in the finish. VICTA WALLY (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
